reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars WORTH IT! Would purchase again
reviews.reviewText: I had initially purchased the lilac case back in April for my 12 pro max. In October the right corner had broken and I completely forgot about it. reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 15, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 3.0 out of 5 stars Great but no mag safe
reviews.reviewText: I enjoy the case. I especially like the color and quality.I have 2 complaints -1- no mag-safe, meaning you have to be rather certain you get the puck for the charger in the right spot, and the magnetic field is not strong and thus doesn’t snap into place. It detaches easily.2- the silicone is great, but has friction when taking it in and out of pockets. It’s great for not sliding out of your back pocket unintentionally, however, putting in pockets is not ideal and takes more time and than I’d prefer.I’m going to keep using the case as I enjoy the quality and especially enjoy the neon color, but next iterations could be improved.
